    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@Blue-Arc `eth_sendTransaction` requires that the node has access to the private key, which is a potential security risk. In Besu we made the conscious decision to not implement this endpoint to avoid that.\r\nThe endpoint is offered by other software like [EthSigner](https://docs.ethsigner.consensys.net/en/stable/) which can be used along side Besu and avoids the exposure of the private key to a node that is connected to the internet.\r\n\r\nI will close this issue, because as mentioned this enpoint is not implemented on purpose.",
